  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Universal Harmony
By: St Isidore
---
No teaching can be perfect without harmony. Indeed, there is nothing in which
it is not found. The world itself is said to be harmoniously formed, and the
very heavens revolve amidst the harmony of the spheres.
